| **Web Application Firewall** | AWS WAF (managed rule groups + custom regex for Uyghur script injection) | Blocks OWASP Top‑10 attacks, including language‑specific XSS payloads. |
| **API Gateway Authorizer** | Lambda authorizer that validates JWTs signed by your IdP (e.g., Cognito) | Guarantees that only authenticated users can invoke backend APIs. |
