| **Immutable Deployments** | Use **CodePipeline** + **CodeBuild** to produce a new Docker image; tag images with a **Git SHA**; never patch in‑place | Guarantees that any change is traceable and reproducible. |
| **Runtime Threat Detection** | Enable **Amazon Inspector** on EC2/ECS; integrate findings into Security Hub | Detects known exploits (e.g., CVE‑2023‑XXXX) before they are leveraged. |
| **Data‑Loss Prevention** | Enable **S3 Object Lock** (compliance mode) on logs and backups | Guarantees that an attacker cannot delete forensic evidence. |

